# Agent Selection Guide

## Engineering Agents
| Problem | Agent |
|---------|-------|
| API design, endpoints, REST | `api-designer` |
| System architecture, patterns | `backend-architect` |
| Queries, indexes, schema | `database-specialist` |
| Bug hunting, root cause | `debugging-specialist` |
| CI/CD, Docker, infra | `devops-engineer` |
| React, Next.js, UI | `frontend-specialist` |
| Translations, localization | `frontend-specialist` + rule `06-i18n` |
| Schema changes, data moves | `migration-specialist` |
| Slow code, memory, latency | `performance-engineer` |
| Auth, vulnerabilities, OWASP | `security-engineer` |
| Screen readers, WCAG, a11y | `accessibility-specialist` |
| Git history, code evolution | `code-archeologist` |

## Testing Agents
| Problem | Agent |
|---------|-------|
| Test strategy, coverage | `test-architect` |
| API/endpoint testing | `api-tester` |
| Browser, Playwright, Cypress | `e2e-tester` |

## Code Quality Agents
| Problem | Agent |
|---------|-------|
| PR review, feedback | `code-reviewer` |
| Code smells, cleanup | `refactoring-expert` |

## Other Agents
| Problem | Agent |
|---------|-------|
| README, docs, ADRs | `technical-writer` |
| Outages, incidents | `incident-responder` |

## Quick Decision Tree
```
Is it broken?
├─ Yes → debugging-specialist
└─ No
   ├─ Is it slow? → performance-engineer
   ├─ Is it insecure? → security-engineer
   ├─ Is it inaccessible? → accessibility-specialist
   ├─ Need to understand history? → code-archeologist
   └─ Building something new?
      ├─ API? → api-designer
      ├─ UI? → frontend-specialist
      ├─ Translations? → frontend-specialist + 06-i18n
      ├─ Database? → database-specialist
      └─ Tests? → test-architect
```
